Subject: Notification: Required Update to your Employee Payroll Portal
Hello,

Our records indicate that your annual tax withholding information (Form W-2/1095-C) requires a mandatory update for the upcoming fiscal quarter. To ensure there are no delays in your payroll processing or direct deposit disbursements, please log in to the Employee Self-Service portal before the Friday deadline.

You can securely update your information at:
https://internal-payroll.hr-benefits-portal.com/auth/login

Thank you for your cooperation.

Corporate Payroll Department
Human Resources Operations
